Hello There!
I see you have installed RegistrationMagic. I am one of the developers of this plugin and we have put countless hours to make it both powerful and easy to use.
We sincerely hope you will enjoy using it. If you run into any problems or have questions, do not hesitate to contact me directly.
Cheers!
